data.description: Welcome to your charming new abode! Situated on a dead-end street, this delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home promises a harmonious blend of comfort and practicality. As you step onto the inviting front landing, you are greeted with warmth, and the backyard beckons as an oasis, boasting both security and privacy within its newly fenced confines, ideal for both pets and loved ones alike. Enjoy a three-tier 35x19 deck, a large 12x16 shed with many useable options, and a designated area for a cozy fire pit, perfect for gatherings under the stars. Alongside the addition of mini-splits to ensure relief from the Cape humidity, there is a new boiler and hot water tank. Moreover, rest easy knowing that the roof and gutters are newer additions, alleviating any concerns about major maintenance expenses. With minimal traffic, this location feels like a true getaway all while enjoying the convenience of being close to everything! Whether it's shopping, dining, schools, or the beach, you're just moments away!
